::DrillBit::

DrillBit was enjoying kissing her, when she passed out.
He cought her, before she collapsed to the floor.
"Hmmm. I think you need to sleep." He picked her up, and carryed her to
bed. He layed her down, and covered her up. He couldn't help but give
her a deep, long kiss.
"Good night. I'll see you in the morning." He turned and walked out, and
back to his quorters, where he went to bed.

OOC: I didn't know what to do. I hope taking her to her bed and all, was
ok.
